==Yin Metal Pig (辛亥)'s Months==
In a {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦}} year whose final digit is 2 or 7 (when the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干}} are {{ill|Ren|ja|壬|1=Mizunoe (壬)}} or {{ill|Tei|ja|丁|1=Hinoto (丁)}}), the month of {{ill|October|ja|10月}} is designated as the {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|月 (暦)}} of {{ill|Xinhai|ja|辛亥}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar}} or to the {{ill|Seasonal Month|ja|節月}} (from {{ill|Beginning of Winter|ja|立冬}} until the day before {{ill|Heavy Snow|ja|大雪}}) as applicable.

