==Yin Metal Pig (辛亥)'s Months==
In a {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦|12=draft|12=draft}} year whose final digit is 2 or 7 (when the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|12=draft|12=draft}} are {{ill|Ren|ja|壬|1=Mizunoe (壬)|12=draft|12=draft}} or {{ill|Tei|ja|丁|1=Hinoto (丁)|12=draft|12=draft}}), the month of {{ill|October|ja|10月|12=draft|12=draft}} is designated as the {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|月 (暦)|12=draft|12=draft}} of {{ill|Xinhai|ja|辛亥|12=draft|12=draft}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft}} or to the {{ill|Seasonal Month|ja|節月|12=draft|12=draft}} (from {{ill|Beginning of Winter|ja|立冬|12=draft|12=draft}} until the day before {{ill|Heavy Snow|ja|大雪|12=draft|12=draft}}) as applicable.

==Yin Metal Pig (辛亥)'s Days==
=== 選日 ===
None.


